   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "261.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "265.080", 
   "id": "s000090", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Was die Arbeitnehmerinnen und Arbeitnehmer wirklich umtreibt: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "265.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "270.760", 
   "id": "s000091", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Konstruktion des Verlagerns des Firmensitzes f\u00fchrt dazu, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "270.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "275.000", 
   "id": "s000092", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass die Rechte nach dem Montan-Mitbestimmungsgesetz, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "275.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "279.200", 
   "id": "s000093", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "mit dem wir seit dem Zweiten Weltkrieg in Deutschland sehr gut gefahren sind, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "279.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "280.480", 
   "id": "s000094", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "gef\u00e4hrdet sind. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "280.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "283.920", 
   "id": "s000095", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dabei ist dies ein Erfolgsmodell in Deutschland. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "283.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "286.400", 
   "id": "s000096", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das wird hier infrage gestellt; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "286.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "291.680", 
   "id": "s000097", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "denn es gibt keine rechtliche Absicherung der Montanmitbestimmung mehr in einem Konzern, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "291.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "296.920", 
   "id": "s000098", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dessen Firmensitz in die Niederlande verlagert wird."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "296.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "298.600", 
   "id": "s000099", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Frage ist: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "298.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "302.240", 
   "id": "s000100", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Warum machen thyssenkrupp und Tata das? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "302.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "306.440", 
   "id": "s000101", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der Grund ist ganz einfach: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "306.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "310.600", 
   "id": "s000102", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie m\u00fcssen in den Niederlanden keine Quellensteuer abf\u00fchren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "310.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "313.880", 
   "id": "s000103", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "was sie aber in Deutschland tun m\u00fcssen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "313.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "315.760", 
   "id": "s000104", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist eine klare L\u00fccke. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "315.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "319.200", 
   "id": "s000105", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir m\u00fcssen daher anstreben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "319.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "323.040", 
   "id": "s000106", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass es kein unterschiedliches Steuerrecht in Europa mehr gibt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "323.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "325.880", 
   "id": "s000107", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir brauchen ein Verbot von solchen Ausnahmen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "325.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "330.080", 
   "id": "s000108", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "von denen die Niederlande hier Gebrauch macht."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "330.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "331.680", 
   "id": "s000109", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich sage Ihnen an dieser Stelle: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "331.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "336.360", 
   "id": "s000110", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Europ\u00e4ische Kommission hat Vorschl\u00e4ge hierzu entwickelt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "336.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "341.480", 
   "id": "s000111", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber die europ\u00e4ischen Finanzminister haben seit Jahren an dieser Stelle nichts hinbekommen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "341.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "345.720", 
   "id": "s000112", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wer bezahlt bitte sch\u00f6n f\u00fcr das jahrelange Nichtstun? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "345.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "352.840", 
   "id": "s000113", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Tag f\u00fcr Tag bezahlen die Arbeitnehmerinnen und Arbeitnehmer in Deutschland knallhart daf\u00fcr, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "352.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "357.080", 
   "id": "s000114", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass an dieser Stelle keine Fortschritte erreicht worden sind. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "357.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "359.200", 
   "id": "s000115", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Panama Papers und Paradise Papers\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "359.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "362.520", 
   "id": "s000116", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "was muss eigentlich noch passieren?"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "362.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "366.840", 
   "id": "s000117", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir merken, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "366.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "374.000", 
   "id": "s000118", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass wir eine neue Koordinierung der Steuerpolitik in Europa brauchen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "374.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "378.760", 
   "id": "s000119", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Auf dem Sondergipfel der europ\u00e4ischen Staats- "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "378.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "385.760", 
   "id": "s000120", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und Regierungschefs vom Wochenende ging es um die soziale Dimension der Europ\u00e4ischen Union, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "385.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "390.400", 
   "id": "s000121", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wozu auch eine gerechte und koordinierte Steuerpolitik, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "390.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "395.520", 
   "id": "s000122", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das Vermeiden von Steuerdumping und das Schlie\u00dfen von Steuerschlupfl\u00f6chern geh\u00f6ren. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "395.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "398.760", 
   "id": "s000123", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wer hat dort mit Abwesenheit gegl\u00e4nzt? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "398.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "399.760", 
   "id": "s000124", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deutschland. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "399.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "404.120", 
   "id": "s000125", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Auf ausdr\u00fccklichen Wunsch der Bundeskanzlerin waren wir dort nicht vertreten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "404.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "410.760", 
   "id": "s000126", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "So kann es nicht weitergehen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "410.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "413.280", 
   "id": "s000127", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir m\u00fcssen uns deshalb daf\u00fcr einsetzen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "413.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "416.280", 
   "id": "s000128", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass Stahlunternehmen in Deutschland bleiben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "416.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "426.120", 
   "id": "s000129", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass die Stahlproduktion in Deutschland und Europa nicht zum Spekulationsobjekt und die entsprechenden Unternehmensbereiche nicht nach dem Willen von einigen Unternehmensentscheidern zur Bad Bank werden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "426.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "430.400", 
   "id": "s000130", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die in diesen Fragen vor allem auf B\u00f6rsenkurse und Renditen schielen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "430.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "432.760", 
   "id": "s000131", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber keinen Wert auf eine nachhaltige Entwicklung legen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "432.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "437.360", 
   "id": "s000132", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir brauchen au\u00dferdem einen aktiven Kampf gegen Steuerdumping. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "437.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "439.440", 
   "id": "s000133", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deswegen ist es an dieser Stelle wichtig, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "439.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "445.760", 
   "id": "s000134", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass der Deutsche Bundestag heute seine Stimme f\u00fcr den Stahlstandort Deutschland und f\u00fcr die Besch\u00e4ftigten im Stahlbereich erhebt."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "445.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "459.000", 
   "id": "s000135", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Als N\u00e4chster hat das Wort Dr.\u00a0Joachim Pfeiffer f\u00fcr die CDU/CSU-Fraktion."
   ]
  }
